data.description: Great home for where you need extra space. When you enter this home there is a formal living room or office area before you enter the extra spacious Kitchen Dining combo and a huge family-room downstairs to entertain your family and friends, Primary bedroom and bath downstairs, 5 nice size bedrooms upstairs with a TV/Game room and a separate office area. Please verify room measurements. This home is close to I-45 and to Hardy Toll Road, close to Restaurants and Shopping centers. Please call for an appointment.
